<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Admin Home - Pet Shop</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .jumbotron {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #007bff; 
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .stat-item {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .stat-item p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .stat-item span {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h2>Bine ai revenit, @Model.nume @Model.prenume!</h2>
        <p>Esti pregatit sa ai grija de animalutele tale?</p>
        <p>Foloseste Navigation Bar-ul pentru a incepe!</p>
        <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <p>@ViewBag.AnimalCount</p>
                <span>Total Animale</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <p>@ViewBag.ComenziCount</p>
                <span>Comenzi in curs</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">

            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Raport", "Admins")">
                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text"></i> Vizualizare Raport
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>